item.title: CVE-2016-9973|2024-08-06T03:07:31.584Z -- ibm -- rational%20collaborative%20lifecycle%20management
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 120209.

item.title: CVE-2016-6024|2024-08-06T01:15:10.795Z -- ibm -- rational%20collaborative%20lifecycle%20management
item.description: IBM Jazz technology based products might divulge information that might be useful in helping attackers through error messages. IBM X-Force ID: 116868.

item.title: CVE-2016-9700|2024-08-06T02:59:03.063Z -- ibm -- rational%20collaborative%20lifecycle%20management
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation could allow an authenticated attacker to obtain sensitive information from error message stack traces. IBM X-Force ID: 119528.
